  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: "Wow!  \n\nYou eliminated the undead threat and discovered the source
      of all the (re)animation happening here."
    nextOption: All in a days work
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'We will need to bring back these crystal samples to the capital.


      One
      of the elder Chanellers there may know why they are animating things.'
    nextOption: So now I can ask the Priestess for help?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Of course.


      There is just one more thing.


      Remember
      how you took an oath to bring the High Priestess cheese?'
    nextOption: Wait, that wasn't a joke?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'You have proved yourself loyal to the SunSworn.


      I''m sure
      the High Priestess would be happy to help you if you bring her a small gift.'
    nextOption: What's with her and cheese anyway?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: It's kind of an open secret that it's not really for her.
    nextOption: Then who's it for?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: She's trying to impress this foreign King who really likes cheese
    nextOption: ...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'There are some mice nearby who may have a little to spare.


      Follow
      the road directly South until you find their camp.'
    nextOption: Yes Sir
